			"value": "<p><em>You create a slippery surface of ice, either on the ground or on the surface of water.</em></p><p><strong>Bonus Action</strong> - 40 ft. Cube (60 ft.) - 10 Minute - Magical</p><ul><li><p>If a creature moves at least 5 ft. across the ice they must succeed on a dexterity saving throw or fall &amp;reference[prone].</p></li><li><p>When this ability ends, the ice rapidly melts unless the ambient temperature is below freezing.</p></li></ul>",
